{"tid":115390,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 聽日去旅行 但係唔見咗本Passport","createTime":"2017-02-10T13:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T10:56:17.000Z","uid":50225,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d51a149496c01eda28901cf043fa97cc48406fa","tid":115390,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"幫嗰好朋友問<br />\n<br />\n話說佢本passport過期，之後佢就去整，咁佢用機整嘅，部機就印晒佢本舊Passport啲資料，之後出咗張紙叫佢幾時拎。到今日去拎啦，點知要帶埋本舊Passport去先拎得(朋友第一次去整)，但佢已經唔記得將本舊Passport擺咗去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果聽日都揾唔到就唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下喺咪可以去報失之後拎住張報失紙去攞翻本新passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9e3c6d3069e339470dcb91a2fc5ebb721b1e91","tid":115390,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:42:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0a8802b9a742fd607ff94ad0810a6d0c5339d0","tid":115390,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:46:51.000Z","msg":"有無bno 有就科水好快搞掂"},{"pid":"897d1fc96d646d8103d5b0063dd3a5b9b6b4c8d3","tid":115390,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無bno 有就科水好快搞掂</blockquote><br />\n無 佢98<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f33c9c43bc73c1abd1d32378d3c6e5801c5c2b6","tid":115390,"uid":50225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a0db324d15e1465e1282e6dddb87cc7425b7bc","tid":115390,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"係咪想我扮入境